com.opengamma.strata.calc.config.pricing

Class DefaultPricingRules

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.calc.config.pricing.DefaultPricingRules
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PricingRules, Bean, ImmutableBean

    public final class DefaultPricingRules
extends Object
implements PricingRules, ImmutableBean
    Pricing rules that combine a list of individual rules.

    These rules combine a list of individual PricingRule instances. It returns the first valid configuration found in the underlying list of rules.
